parameters.description: Array of processor parameters. More details are given below

type.description: The type of processor. Valid Values: `RecordDeAggregation`, `Lambda`, `MetadataExtraction`, `AppendDelimiterToRecord`. Validation is done against [AWS SDK constants](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/sdk-for-go/api/service/firehose/#pkg-constants); so that values not explicitly listed may also work.
